abstract: Matthew Fitzpatrick wins British Masters golf tournament, his first professional title.
lead_paragraph: Matthew Fitzpatrick signaled his emergence as one of Europe’s most prominent young golfers, shooting a three-under 68 to complete a wire-to-wire victory in the British Masters in Woburn, England, for his first professional title.
